sentences.sentence: The filter-through of stimulus cash to the pachinko parlours has historical precedent.

sentences.sentence: Pachinko stocks were the best-performing equities in the market over the following six months.
sentences.translation: 帕金宫股票是接下来6个月中市场表现最好的一支股票。

sentences.sentence: They will help you determine how much of your cash you want to put into the online Pachinko machine.
